# ==============================================================================
# NOTES
# ==============================================================================
# - For local development: Use DATABASE_URL with localhost
# - For Docker: Use docker-compose.yml and the same DATABASE_URL
# - For production: Use managed PostgreSQL (AWS RDS, Supabase, etc.) with SSL enabled
# - pgvector extension is required for RAG functionality
